<item>
            <title>[LU-14455] mdt_dom_resource_prolong() can miss needed lock</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14455</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;mdt_dom_resource_prolong() should find all locks on the resource to prolong them when needed but it stops after the first one found. That is not correct because found lock could be even from different export and mdt_rw_hpreq_check() will end with &lt;tt&gt;-ESTALE&lt;/tt&gt; error wrongly&lt;/p&gt;</description>
